{
  "stem": "15694.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very hard work and lots to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, you can imagine I got very, very strong, which probably helped me for the later camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's not much to tell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have been nine months there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "During that time, was not a single person killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was at the 20th of July when we heard about Hitler, the-- the main attack on Hitler's life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it made not a slightest difference to us-- to us whether-- what happening somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever happened, it happened somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It didn't happen-- nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It went on, the daily routine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In any case, in the end it was to be found out he wasn't killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Except as we learned later, quite a number of people have been hanged on-- you know, with-- with wire, some of them Hitler's friends, even.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a blanket and-- well, straw mattresses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The food I just mentioned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In this particular camp, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody killed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hard work, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- very interesting that you ask me that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have been asked-- I've been interviewed by the Imperial War Museum on 26 reels.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he asked that question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the-- I have completely, as I have so many things which I have forgotten.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Amongst them the sanitary arrangement in most camps, except the latrines in Plaszow, and later-- which at the end of my story, the toilets in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now I can't remember it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it is nothing special to talk about.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in barracks, and we were-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You know, what else to say?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were not beaten.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
